<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>Hanson的生活博客</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life</link><description>Hanson and 睿 are Friend!</description><copyright>Hanson的生活博客</copyright><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/157664656?v=4</url><title>avatar</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Jun 2025 07:50:44 +0000</lastBuildDate><managingEditor>Hanson的生活博客</managingEditor><ttl>60</ttl><webMaster>Hanson的生活博客</webMaster><item><title>星座和人格只是个工具</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/xing-zuo-he-ren-ge-zhi-shi-ge-gong-ju.html</link><description>不要用星座和人格定义或限制你的性格，他们只是个工具。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/xing-zuo-he-ren-ge-zhi-shi-ge-gong-ju.html</guid><pubDate>Sat, 28 Jun 2025 07:50:18 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>那些象征着区别对待的记忆，每次想起，都犹如利箭穿心</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/na-xie-xiang-zheng-zhao-qu-bie-dui-dai-de-ji-yi-%EF%BC%8C-mei-ci-xiang-qi-%EF%BC%8C-du-you-ru-li-jian-chuan-xin.html</link><description>那些象征着区别对待的记忆，在脑海里挥之不去，每次想起，都犹如利箭穿心，重点转移，关系变淡的想法也愈发强烈，哎，难受。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/na-xie-xiang-zheng-zhao-qu-bie-dui-dai-de-ji-yi-%EF%BC%8C-mei-ci-xiang-qi-%EF%BC%8C-du-you-ru-li-jian-chuan-xin.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 16:14:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>和睿看电影</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/he-rui-kan-dian-ying.html</link><description>因为有了时间的存在，才让我们更懂得珍惜，永生故好，但往往会留下更多遗憾。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/he-rui-kan-dian-ying.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 16:02:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>空耳唯一</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/kong-er-wei-yi.html</link><description>有时候总感觉我和他关系已经淡了，要不是他优先找廖邵他们，要么是他只对其他人“犯贱”，要么是允许别人对他勾肩搭背以至于以同样的方式回应，而排斥我这样做，而且他对我勾肩搭背和锁喉的次数也减少了，要么单独和邵廖他们去“散步”去食堂，要么坐在邵的座位上，被邵坐在下面，却搂着邵，哎，口头上说着最重要，唯一(之前说的)，但在现在总感觉这些话成了空耳，也许，我在他的世界里成了个配角吧，如果这是真的，我希望这是一场梦，更希望它快点醒来，使我的心灵免受情感之痛。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/kong-er-wei-yi.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 14:05:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>当回忆冲进大脑（DeepSeek）</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/dang-hui-yi-chong-jin-da-nao-%EF%BC%88DeepSeek%EF%BC%89.html</link><description>当回忆冲进大脑，强烈的负面过往总能刺穿当下的心境；而曾经的美好，若被置于失去的背景下，也会在怀念中化作利刃。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/dang-hui-yi-chong-jin-da-nao-%EF%BC%88DeepSeek%EF%BC%89.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 11:44:02 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>一张纸被撕了，就不能回到原来的样子，镜子碎了，也很难再恢复</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/yi-zhang-zhi-bei-si-le-%EF%BC%8C-jiu-bu-neng-hui-dao-yuan-lai-de-yang-zi-%EF%BC%8C-jing-zi-sui-le-%EF%BC%8C-ye-hen-nan-zai-hui-fu.html</link><description>一张纸被撕了，就不能回到原来的样子，镜子碎了，也很难再恢复，原来所受的创伤，会以希望和要求的形式寄托在下一位重要朋友的身上，我进入一段关系很容易，但让我抛弃一段关系（决裂），我很难做到，就像伏地魔失去一件魂器一样。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/yi-zhang-zhi-bei-si-le-%EF%BC%8C-jiu-bu-neng-hui-dao-yuan-lai-de-yang-zi-%EF%BC%8C-jing-zi-sui-le-%EF%BC%8C-ye-hen-nan-zai-hui-fu.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 11:39:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>我与他们（有感而发）</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/wo-yu-ta-men-%EF%BC%88-you-gan-er-fa-%EF%BC%89.html</link><description>“唯一”一词成为了空耳，优先人的改变，友谊的变化，都隐隐暗藏着扎人的事实，行为上的拒绝，交流的减少，他不再是因为想我而交流，更多的则是有事找我。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/wo-yu-ta-men-%EF%BC%88-you-gan-er-fa-%EF%BC%89.html</guid><pubDate>Sat, 21 Jun 2025 15:42:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>博客建好辣！</title><link>https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/bo-ke-jian-hao-la-%EF%BC%81.html</link><description>于2025/4/18重建博客。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://Hanson-zhy.github.io/blog-life/post/bo-ke-jian-hao-la-%EF%BC%81.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 11:44:40 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>